Daniel Sturridge salva lil Liverpool minn telf fil-Premier League kontra Chelsea bil-goal li għamel fil-minuta 89 nhar is-Sibt f'Stamford Bridge, Londra.
Sturridge rċieva pass minn Xherdan Shaqiri madwar 27 metru mill-porteria ta 'Chelsea meta t-tim tiegħu kienet qed tifla' 1-0.
